This Sample have bellow function.

1. Have implemented authentication
   .twitter oauth 1.0 
   .facebook oauth 2.0
   .foursquare oauth 2.0
in rhodes(3.3.3).
   
2. after sign in save the access token in local mobile phone database.

3. post status by access token which store in database.

4. it test successful in android 2.3.4

Note:
Facebook App's Mobile Web URL  should be set to : "http://redirectme.to"
FourSquare App's Callback url should be set to :  "http://redirectme.to"

Facebook access token will expire date is 2 months.
So before access token expire please request user relogin 
the facebook in your mobile app and then can get a new long-lived(2 months)
access token.